GroovyKotlin build.gradle<pre><code>dependencies {
implementation 'androidx.hilt:hilt-work:1.0.0'
// When using Kotlin.
kapt 'androidx.hilt:hilt-compiler:1.0.0'
// When using Java.
annotationProcessor 'androidx.hilt:hilt-compiler:1.0.0'
}
</code></pre> build.gradle.kts<pre><code>dependencies {
implementation("androidx.hilt:hilt-work:1.0.0")
// When using Kotlin.
kapt("androidx.hilt:hilt-compiler:1.0.0")
// When using Java.
annotationProcessor("androidx.hilt:hilt-compiler:1.0.0")
}
</code></pre>

GroovyKotlin <pre><code>dependencies {
implementation "androidx.startup:startup-runtime:1.1.1"
}
</code></pre> <pre><code>dependencies {
implementation("androidx.startup:startup-runtime:1.1.1")
}
</code></pre>

GroovyKotlin <pre><code>android {
buildFeatures {
compose true
}
composeOptions {
kotlinCompilerExtensionVersion = "1.3.2"
}
}
</code></pre> <pre><code>android {
buildFeatures {
compose = true
}
composeOptions {
kotlinCompilerExtensionVersion = "1.3.2"
}
}
</code></pre> <ul> <li><code>buildFeatures</code> 블록 내에서 <code>compose</code> 플래그를 <code>true</code>로 설정하면 <code>compose</code> 기능을 활성화합니다.</li> <li><code>composeOptions</code> 블록에 정의된 <code>kotlinCompilerExtensionVersion</code>는 Kotlin 버전 관리에 연관되어 있습니다. 여기를 참고하여 프로젝트의 Kotlin 버전과 일치하는 버전을 선택해야 합니다.</li> </ul>
